{"tid":1717821,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好撚再討論對家傷者","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:36:32.000Z","uid":87582,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"faa9b72eba2c8c28b729e527687c1844444d4567","tid":1717821,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"我地要做係做文宣<br />\n甚至要大家一路都記住我地有幾多人受傷<br />\n唔好再理對家點<br />\n<br />\n文宣係幫助我地講返件事<br />\n希望前幾個月文宣組一路做嘅野會出現返<br />\n本地 外國都要<br />\n木本要講射tg已經污染左香港飲用水<br />\n藍絲都會驚依啲野<br />\n<br />\n我唔該你地再睇清楚要點行啦條路<br />\n路好好再比風向撚帶到<br />\n要記住我地有好多人做左好多野甚至離開左我地<br />\n<br />\n唔好再見到有人比人圍唔上去幫<br />\n我地優勢係人數 要講幾撚多次先識做<br />\n要講幾手"},{"pid":"8c835510a4701a90621d4da8b3739bd1fd339ad7","tid":1717821,"uid":87582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好再一樣野出幾十個post<br />\n出之前搵下有無出過係咪咁撚難？"},{"pid":"c36f7a14590576a45354de9153409ab8170c99ab","tid":1717821,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"[和你勇文宣升級！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嬲好嬲好嬲，但文宣更要做好，要拉攏最多人過黎同對方憾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7f8d7955920fdbd31a587f61f416dc6c8991dab","tid":1717821,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"講左好多